queries.sql: SELECT `dbt_nfts_store`.*, `dbt_user`.`f_name`, `dbt_user`.`l_name`, `dbt_user`.`wallet_address`, `dbt_nft_category`.`cat_name`, `dbt_nft_collection`.`title` as `collection_title`, SUM(`dbt_earnings`.`amount`) AS `amount` FROM `dbt_nfts_store` LEFT JOIN `dbt_user` ON `dbt_user`.`user_id`=`dbt_nfts_store`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `dbt_nft_category` ON `dbt_nft_category`.`id`=`dbt_nfts_store`.`category_id` LEFT JOIN `dbt_nft_collection` ON `dbt_nft_collection`.`id`=`dbt_nfts_store`.`collection_id` LEFT JOIN `dbt_earnings` ON `dbt_earnings`.`nft_id`=`dbt_nfts_store`.`id` WHERE `dbt_earnings`.`amount` > 0 GROUP BY `dbt_earnings`.`nft_id` ORDER BY `id` DESC LIMIT 10
